text: Kristína Košíková (born 20 December 1993) is a Slovak footballer who plays as a midfielder for Czech club Slovan Liberec and the Slovakia women's national team. ==References== Category:1993 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Slovak women's footballers Category:Slovakia women's international footballers Category:Slovak expatriate footballers Category:Slovak expatriate sportspeople in the Czech Republic Category:Expatriate women's footballers in the Czech Republic Category:FK Slovan Duslo Šaľa (women) players Category:ŠK Slovan Bratislava (women) players
